headline: DIGIORNO® AND HIDDEN VALLEY® RANCH LAUNCH TWO RANCH-FORWARD PIZZAS THAT BRING PIZZA AND RANCH TOGETHER LIKE NEVER BEFORE
summary: DiGiorno® and Hidden Valley® Ranch know that pizza and ranch isn't just a pairing, it's a lifestyle. That is why they are teaming up to take this obsession to the next level with two bold, ranchified pizza creations that bring the fan-favorite duo to life like never before.

headline: Clorox Declares Regular Quarterly Dividend of $1.22 Per Share
summary: The Clorox Company (NYSE: CLX) announced today that its board of directors has declared a quarterly dividend of $1.22 per share on the company's common stock. The dividend is payable May 9, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on April 23, 2025.
